    {
      "id": "q-sw",
      "navLabel": "Service Worker",
      "question": "Service Worker 能做什么？",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "运行在"
          },
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "独立线程"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "，可拦截网络请求做缓存（PWA 离线包）、推送通知后台同步；生命周期 "
